ModEntry.Name: MGO headgear fovaInfo mod
ModEntry.Author: tinmantex
ModEntry.Description:
MGO headgear fovaInfo mod r1 For Infinite Heaven r202+
Mostly just full MGO helmets that works without any modification, mostly full headgear.
1. Install 'MGO headgear fovaInfo.mgsv' with snakebite. 2. Copy mod\fovaInfo\mgoHeadgear_fovaInfo.lua to MGS_TPP\mod\fovaInfo
In Infinite Heaven menu Player settings > Appearance menu Change 'Filter faces' option to 'Head fova mods' Then chose head in 'Face' option.
